fulltitle: Dave Brubeck and Sons on The Buck Matthews Show
description: Two Generations of Brubeck performs live in studio on The Buck Matthews Show on WOTV8, Grand Rapids, Michigan, circa 1973-ish.  Also includes a great interview. For more on Buck visit www.buckmatthews.com
